eat availability without which we would have lost our day in Nha Trang following the closure of part of the Vinpearl complex.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Good luck and see you soon for another trip!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Patrick and his family</p>\r\n', null, '1', null, '0', '0', '5.0', '0', null, '', '', '2015-08-08 00:00:00', '2017-11-28 02:22:35', '6', '6');
